genresAdvancedInfo.name: choro contemporaneo
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A modern take on the traditional Brazilian choro genre. It incorporates elements of jazz and other contemporary styles, while still maintaining the virtuosic instrumental performances and improvisation that are hallmarks of the original genre.
